  02 Apr 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> bcel-5.1-r1.ebuild,
  -bcel-5.1.ebuild:
  cleanup, removed old revision with a dependency to regexp.

*bcel-5.1-r1 27 Mar 2005

  27 Mar 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> +bcel-5.1-r1.ebuild:
  moved from dev-java/regexp to dev-java/jakarta-regexp dependency. see #71336.
  introduced support for the source useflag.

  26 Jan 2005; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> bcel-5.1.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc64

  16 Jan 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> bcel-5.1.ebuild:
  added app-arch/unzip to DEPEND, fixes #78170.

  30 Dec 2004; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org>
  +files/bcel-5.1-gentoo-buildxml.diff, +files/bcel-5.1-gentoo-src.diff,
  bcel-5.1.ebuild:
  Added support for JDK 1.5, thanks to Jan Brinkmann <luck@the-luckyduck.de>.
  Fixes #73319.

  18 Dec 2004; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> bcel-5.1.ebuild:
